A quick tutorial on how to use selenium with the chromedriver in Python on the Heroku platform. Article version with code: https://www.andressevilla.com/running-chromedriver-with-python-selenium-on-heroku/

==Buildpacks==
https://github.com/heroku/heroku-buildpack-google-chrome
https://github.com/heroku/heroku-buildpack-chromedriver

==Environment Variables==
CHROMEDRIVER_PATH = /app/.chromedriver/bin/chromedriver
GOOGLE_CHROME_BIN = /app/.apt/usr/bin/google-chrome